Revision history for IPC-MicroSocket

0.04    2026-01-29
        [CHANGES]
         * Provide a `->new_inprocess` client constructor for convenience of
           in-process client setups

0.03    2025-07-11
        [CHANGES]
         * Provide abstract classes (as per Object::Pad v0.817) rather than
           roles

        [BUGFIXES]
         * Make sure to pass other named arguments from Server->new_unix
           wrapper to the actual class constructor

0.02    2024-08-15
        [CHANGES]
         * Use named parameter support of Sublike::Extended

        [BUGFIXES]
         * Need `Test::future::IO` v0.06 to get the `->expect_accept` method

0.01    2024-08-05
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.
